        "heading": "Why Tarelcraft was founded",
        "founder_title": "Founder",
        "story": "<p>I founded TARELCRAFT because I believe in real memories — not mass-produced gifts or generic presents.<br/><br/>I wanted to create something that <strong>lasts</strong>, something that truly touches people and makes them smile, laugh, or even cry.</p><p>I've seen how hard it is to find a gift that’s truly personal.<br/><br/>One that says: <em>“I thought about you. I see you.”</em><br/><br/>That’s where the idea began: <strong>A gift that doesn’t just surprise — but connects.</strong></p><p>At TARELCRAFT, we create figurines that are more than decoration.<br/><br/>Each one is <strong>handcrafted and custom-modeled from your photos</strong>, made with care and shipped with love.</p><p>What makes us different?<br/><br/>We don’t just tell a story — <strong>we tell YOUR story</strong>.<br/><br/>Whether it’s a memory, a symbol of love, or a celebration of a unique moment — every custom figurine reflects something real, something personal.</p><p>TARELCRAFT is more than just a store.<br/><br/>It’s a space for emotion. For creativity. For your story in 3D.</p>",
